@startuml
title Plugin Execution
actor Operator
participant Main
participant Registry
participant Config
participant Plugin
participant Pipeline
participant Repository
Operator -> Main : command
Main -> Registry : require enabled
Main -> Config : resolve
Config --> Main : ApplicationConfig
Main -> Plugin : validate
Main -> Pipeline : execute
Pipeline -> Plugin : hooks
Pipeline -> Repository : load
Repository --> Pipeline : ImportResult
Pipeline --> Main : result
Main --> Operator : status/duration
@enduml
